knowledge for the future studies on TSN real-time\nscheduling problems, and serve as the performance benchmarking for scheduling\nmethod development in TSN.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 26 May 2023 09:33:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-29"}
